Whole Body Benefits: Our complete multivitamin comes packed with 24 vitamins and minerals to support your energy, immunity, and overall health, including high potency, activated B vitamins -- all in just 2 capsules a day.*

Plant-Based Nutrients: We believe that the best nutrition comes from nature, not from a lab. Our multivitamins are made with friendly, plant-based vitamins and minerals like vitamin D3 from lichen, vitamin E from sunflower, and calcium from marine algae.

Organic Fruits & Veggies: Our Whole Food Multivitamins include a blend of real, organic fruits and vegetables for an extra boost of whole food nutrition, featuring a colorful spectrum of superfoods like beets, carrots, blueberries, and kale.

No Nonsense: We like to keep it clean. All NATURELO Whole Food Multivitamins are non-GMO and vegan-friendly, with no added preservatives, coloring, or flavoring, and no gluten, dairy, or soy. And all NATURELO supplements are lab-tested for purity and potency.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: NATURELO has a unique approach to formulating our supplements — we always use the cleanest most bioavailable ingredients whenever possible so that you can get the most benefit from each supplement. We seek out plant-based nutrients which means sourcing vitamin E from sunflowers (instead of synthetics), Vitamin D from lichen (instead of animal based lanolin which comes from sheep grease!) and Calcium from marine algae (instead of cheaper calcium carbonate which is actually made from rocks!) If that isn’t enough, we also boost our supplements with proprietary blends of organic fruits, vegetables and botanicals for an extra source of real whole food nutrition. Like organic broccoli, carrots, blueberries, kale, spinach, heart healthy turmeric, immune boosting mushrooms… we could go on and on and on.... Naturelo... from Nature with Love

Plant-Based Nutrition Real food ingredients grown in sunshine, water, and soil. Keepin’ it Clean Non-GMO with no artificial preservatives or additives. Whole Body Health Support for your energy, health, and well-being. 3rd Party Verified Made in a GMP-audited facility and lab tested for purity.

Whole Body Wellness Real beauty starts on the inside with whole body wellness. Our complete multivitamin comes packed with 24 vitamins and minerals to nourish your overall health and vitality – including some extra love for your hair, skin, and nails from high potency biotin and vitamin C.* Our multis are made with friendly, plant-based vitamins and minerals, like vitamin D3 from lichen, vitamin E from sunflower, and calcium from marine algae. Beauty from Within* Nourish your natural beauty from the inside out with ingredients that help protect, hydrate, and renew skin from within.* Our special Beauty Blend features hyaluronic acid, a naturally occurring protein in the skin that helps keep skin hydrated and plump. It also provides an extra boost of antioxidant power from glutathione, organic grape seed extract, and organic spirulina to help protect against free radical damage cells and contribute to signs of aging.* Whole Food Nutrition Raise your hand if you eat enough fruits and veggies every day. We hear you. Our Whole Food Multivitamin includes a blend of real, organic fruits and vegetables for an extra boost of whole food nutrition. It’s got a colorful spectrum of nature’s goodness, including beets, carrots, blueberries, spinach, pomegranate, and kale. Not only are the fruits and veggies organic, our multivitamins are completely non-GMO and vegan, with no preservatives added.
